content:
The Analytics for Communications-Business app provides a comprehensive range of B2B business analytics, starting from opportunity, quote, order completion, and fulfillment insights to enhance sales and operational efficiency. It simplifies the complex enterprise quoting process through visualizations and provides SMB executives with a complete account 360 view.

Home Embedded Dashboard helps you stay on top of communications sales processes details with a comprehensive dashboard showing opportunities, quotes, and orders information.

Account Insights embedded dashboard embeds your account information anywhere, providing details about opportunities, quotes, and orders for an account to optimize selling.

Quote Insights dashboard is designed to be embedded wherever quotes are tracked, quickly and easily understanding where efforts should be put.

Self-Service Embedded Dashboard offers a comprehensive view of account-specific details, including contracts, quotes, orders, bills, and asset distribution. Procurement Managers can access this dashboard in the community portal for a 360Â° view of the complete account.

Quote to Order Process Visualization dashboard provides B2B Sales Agents with a comprehensive and clear view of their Quote to Order progress, gaining insights into missing details required for task completion and identifying focus areas to streamline the process effectively.

Report Download Dashboard allows users to view and download customer-specific reports for every stage of the Quote to Order process, offering a comprehensive view of the stage's status and highlighting any missing or partially valid data.
title: Using CRM Analytics Dashboards
